#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:57
msgid "Who We Are"
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:60
msgid "Nezer Motors is a Nyeri-based automotive group that owns and operates two vehicle service brands: AutoCare Express and QwikFix. Both branches serve drivers across Nyeri and the wider Central Kenya region with professional, reliable car care."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:62
msgid "Founded on the belief that vehicle owners deserve honest information, quality parts, and skilled technicians, Nezer Motors has built a reputation for consistent service. Whether you need a full engine overhaul or a quick wheel alignment, our teams handle it with care."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:64
msgid "Each branch maintains its own specialist team, giving you access to a broader range of automotive expertise under one trusted group name."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:73
msgid "Honest Service"
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:73
msgid "We tell you exactly what your vehicle needs — no upsells, no surprises."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:74
msgid "Quality Parts"
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:74
msgid "Genuine, approved components for every repair and service we carry out."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:75
msgid "Skilled Techs"
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:75
msgid "Trained technicians with hands-on experience across all major vehicle makes."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:76
msgid "Fair Pricing"
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:76
msgid "Transparent pricing before work begins. No hidden charges, ever."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:129
msgid "Mechanical Expertise at Kingongo"
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:132
msgid "AutoCare Express is our full mechanical service branch at Kingongo, opposite GK Prison in Nyeri. The team handles everything from routine repairs to complex engine overhauls, working on all major vehicle brands."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:135
msgid "With trained technicians and the right tools for the job, AutoCare Express delivers work that lasts. We stock genuine parts and give customers a clear picture of what their vehicle needs before any work begins."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:168
msgid "Tyres, Alignment & More at Shell Station"
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:171
msgid "QwikFix operates from Shell Service Station on the Nyeri-Nyahururu Road. The branch specialises in wheel-related services, batteries, tyre sales and car accessories, making it the go-to stop for drivers heading in and out of Nyeri."
msgstr ""

#: theme/page-templates/page-about.php:174
